{"tid":2294099,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"投資陷阱｜八旬腦退化用支銀既後果 婆婆被游說網上買基金1個月痛蝕46萬 揭中銀經理違規銷售","createTime":"2020-11-20T18:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T18:07:56.000Z","uid":18381,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8daea04609c641f5062e13b5cd014ab599c791d","tid":2294099,"uid":18381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T18:06:00.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎重創百業包括銀行界，銀行職員為賺佣不惜向退休人士力銷中高風險基金，銀髮族易成受害人。金管局透露今年52宗銀行職員涉不當銷售投資產品的投訴之中，有11名受害人為65歲或以上長者。《蘋果》近日即收到投訴，有八旬婆婆雖然患腦化症兼不諳電腦使用，但今年2月仍被中銀職員游說重設了網上戶口密碼並即日進行3宗網上基金交易，結果一個月內痛蝕46萬。家人追查後發現，婆婆過去7年內原來已在銀行職員游說下曾進行近30宗基金交易，交易頻繁，令婆婆累計要承擔多達21萬手續費，家人質疑有人為賺佣金不擇手段。中銀經調查後承認，一名客戶經理在處理網上基金交易時違反銀行內部指引，銀行願承擔婆婆部份損失，消息更指該經理已離職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201120/SEXTTK7P3VEH7AWAGRDLAGSHGE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR17Mgkf73e1gWQ36s7Jmia4B3_77Xz1D6dixx0xt-Paggy2HiBeW6XKirU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201120%2FSEXTTK7P3VEH7AWAGRDLAGSHGE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR17Mgkf73e1gWQ36s7Jmia4B3_77Xz1D6dixx0xt-Paggy2HiBeW6XKirU&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM35SOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=03bed96d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201120%2FSEXTTK7P3VEH7AWAGRDLAGSHGE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR17Mgkf73e1gWQ36s7Jmia4B3_77Xz1D6dixx0xt-Paggy2HiBeW6XKirU&h=42a5875a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201120/SEXTTK7P3VEH7AWAGRDLAGSHGE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR17Mgkf73e1gWQ36s7Jmia4B3_77Xz1D6dixx0xt-Paggy2HiBeW6XKirU</a><br />\n<br />\n老人家既錢都呃<im